	Sir Palomedes	Fenrir	*male	12. A knight in Ireland who is in love with La Belle Isault. He becomes an adversary to Sir Tristram and is defeated by him in a tournament.
	Sir Bleoberis de Ganis	Onyx	*male	12. A knight of the Round Table and cousin to Sir Lancelot. He takes a lady from King Mark's court, leading to conflict with Sir Tristram.
	Sir Sagramour le Desirous	Puck	*male	12. A knight of King Arthur's court who is defeated by Sir Tristram in battle.
	Sir Dodinas le Savage	Daniel	*male	12. A knight of King Arthur's court who is defeated by Sir Tristram in battle.
	Sir Andret	Michael	*male	12. A knight who plots against Sir Tristram and is defeated by him in battle.
