	Queen Guinevere	Sarah	female	13. The queen of King Arthur, who is deeply affected by Lancelot's departure for the quest. | 14. The queen of Camelot, married to King Arthur. She is deeply in love with Sir Lancelot but becomes angry and jealous when she believes he is neglecting her. She accuses him of disloyalty, leading to his departure from court. | 15. The queen of Britain and wife of King Arthur. She is the catalyst for much of the conflict, accused of dishonoring her husband and ultimately rescued by Lancelot.
